lle, Wedge Plantation, 8 Apr. 1970, D.C. Ferguson; 69, Lacinipolia explicata, f, Maryland, Anne Arundel Co., South Haven, 15 Aug. 1992, H.G. Stevenson; 70, Lacinipolia implicata, f, Tennessee, Cocke Co., Foothills Parkway, second overlook East, 21 Sep. 2000, D. &amp; M. Davis, USNMENT 00153263; 71, Lacinipolia implicata, m, Tennessee, Cocke Co., Foothills Parkway, second overlook East, 21 Sep. 2000, D. &amp; M. Davis, USNMENT 00153261; 72, Lacinipolia implicata, m, Tennessee, Cocke Co., Foothills Parkway, second overlook East, 21 Sep. 2000, D. &amp; M. Davis, USNMENT 00153260." figureDoi-0="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5312396" figureDoi-1="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5312398" httpUri-0="https://zenodo.org/record/5312396/files/figure.png" httpUri-1="https://zenodo.org/record/5312398/files/figure.png" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">Figs. 64–65</figureCitation>
